# Summary
This documentation page explains how to define goals for experiments in Amplitude Experiment, including setting primary and secondary metrics, choosing experiment types (hypothesis testing or do-no-harm), and creating or editing metrics. It emphasizes the importance of selecting appropriate metrics that directly measure the user actions affected by the experiment variants.

